    {
      "text": "“The risk of contracting a disease increases if profit is valued more than health”. This statement represents which of the following theories in sociology?",
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": 0,
          "text": "Feminist theory"
        },
        {
          "id": 1,
          "text": "Parsonian theory"
        },
        {
          "id": 2,
          "text": "Foucauldian theory"
        },
        {
          "id": 3,
          "text": "Marxist theory"
        }
      ],
      "correct_choice_id": 3,
      "solution": "<p><strong>Answer: D) Marxist theory.</strong></p>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p><strong>Explanation:</strong></p>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p><strong>Theories in sociology:</strong></p>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<table align=\"center\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse; width:694px\">\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Marxist theory</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li style=\"text-align: center;\">Putting profit as a priority instead of health</li>\n\t\t\t\t<li style=\"text-align: center;\">Eg: Alcohol and tobacco consumption is not completely banned as it leads to loss of revenue</li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Parsonian theory</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li style=\"text-align: center;\">Social factors like poverty, migration and industrialisation playing a role in disease etiology</li>\n\t\t\t\t<li style=\"text-align: center;\">Eg, TB due to overcrowding from poverty</li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Feminist theory</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li style=\"text-align: center;\">Females are enforced by <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"e48bb8abfa1692777192e3fa06774f\">men</span> to do particular roles</li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Foucauldian theory</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li style=\"text-align: center;\">By segregating the population into groups, they can be controlled easily</li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Mckeown’s theory of TB</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li style=\"text-align: center;\">Changes in socio-environmental conditions lead to a reduction in TB</li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>",
