    {
      "text": "A couple with three children lives in a small town. The first child of the couple travels abroad for his studies. The above family is in which phase of the family cycle?",
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": 0,
          "text": "Extension"
        },
        {
          "id": 1,
          "text": "Complete extension"
        },
        {
          "id": 2,
          "text": "Contraction"
        },
        {
          "id": 3,
          "text": "Dissolution"
        }
      ],
      "correct_choice_id": 2,
      "solution": "<p><strong>Answer: C) Contraction</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>Explanation:</strong></p>\n\n<p>A family is a biological, social, and cultural unit consisting of people who are biologically related and share a common kitchen. The<strong> life cycle</strong> of the family is the <strong>process and stages</strong> that a family typically goes through in its life course. </p>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p><strong>Family life cycle:</strong></p>\n\n<table align=\"center\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse; width:699px\">\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:middle\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Phases of Family Cycle</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:middle\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Events taking place</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:middle\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Beginning of phase</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:middle\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>End of phase</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:middle\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>1. Formation</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:middle\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\">Marriage</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:middle\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\">Birth of 1st child</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:middle\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>2. Extension </strong>(Option A)</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:middle\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\">Birth of 1st child</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:middle\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\">Birth of last child</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:middle\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>3. Complete extension</strong><strong> </strong>(Option B)</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:middle\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\">Birth of last child</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:middle\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\">1st child leaves home</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:middle\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>4. Contraction</strong> (Option C)</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:middle\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\">1st child leaves home</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:middle\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\">Last child leaves home</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:middle\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>5. Completed contraction</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:middle\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\">Last child leaves home</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:middle\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\">1st spouse dies</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:middle\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>6. <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"1924dd4c6e169277718654d32a636f\">Dissolution</span> </strong>(Option D)</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:middle\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\">1st spouse dies</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:middle\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\">Death of the survivor (extinction)</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>",
