    {
      "text": "Mr. Sharma's family consists of four members. Mr. Sharma is a graduate working as a manager in a private company, earning a monthly income of INR 50,000. Mrs. Sharma is a high school graduate and a homemaker, and their two children are school students.\n\nBased on the Modified Kuppuswamy Scale, what is the socio-economic status of Mr. Sharma's family?",
