      "solution": "<p><strong>Answer: C) The Udai Pareek Scale is used in rural areas.</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>Explanation:</strong></p>\n\n<table align=\"center\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"width:650px\">\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-color:#000000; border-style:solid\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Parameters</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-color:#000000; border-style:solid\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Udai Pareek Scale</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-color:#000000; border-style:solid\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>BG Prasad Scale</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-color:#000000; border-style:solid\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Purpose</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-color:#000000; border-style:solid\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\">Use in rural areas</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-color:#000000; border-style:solid\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\">Applicable to both rural and urban areas</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-color:#000000; border-style:solid\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Components</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-color:#000000; border-style:solid\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\">Independent of income</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-color:#000000; border-style:solid\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\">Based on per <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"ea701c975f169277718359559b503c\">capita</span> income</p>\n\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\">Per <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"ea701c975f169277718359559b503c\">capita</span> income = Total family income/ Number of family members</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-color:#000000; border-style:solid\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Other Parameters</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-color:#000000; border-style:solid\">\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li>Caste</li>\n\t\t\t\t<li>Occupation</li>\n\t\t\t\t<li>Education</li>\n\t\t\t\t<li>Land</li>\n\t\t\t\t<li>Social participation</li>\n\t\t\t\t<li>House</li>\n\t\t\t\t<li>Farm power</li>\n\t\t\t\t<li>Material possessions</li>\n\t\t\t\t<li>Family members</li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-color:#000000; border-style:solid\">\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li>Divides into upper, middle, and lower classes. </li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>",
